Class InstructorModel

  • java.lang.Object
    • CSTutor.Model.Progress.InstructorModel

  • public class InstructorModel
extends java.lang.Object
    Class Student is a model class for the Calendar Tool progress and assessment feature. It contains methods for all of the operations defined for Student users, including retrieving data from the database.
